ekaw#Event: The social event is the parent of conferencebanquet and scientificevent.
ekaw#Person: The parent of a student is the student, the student is the student and the agency staff member is the parent of the paperauthor and the possiblereviewer. The pcmember and the scmember are both parents of the conferenceparticipant and the demochair.
ekaw#Accepted_Paper: Acceptedpaper is the child of evaluatedpaper and the parent of rejectedpaper.
ekaw#Rejected_Paper: The rejected paper is the child of the evaluated paper and the accepted paper.
ekaw#Evaluated_Paper: The evaluation paper is the parent of acceptedpaper and rejectedpaper. The paper is also the child of submittedpaper and evaluatedpaper. The review and neutralreview are both parents of evaluatedpaper.
ekaw#Camera_Ready_Paper: camerareadypaper is a child of paper which is the parent of industrialpaper.
ekaw#Positive_Review: positivereview is a child of review and is parented by a website.
ekaw#Workshop_Paper: The workshoppaper is a child of paper which is the parent of the multiauthor volume.
ekaw#Industrial_Paper: Industrialpaper is a child of paper which is the parent of a website.
ekaw#Paper: Paper is the parent of workshoppaper, programmebrochure, conferencepaper and industrialpaper.
ekaw#Conference_Paper: Conferencepaper is the child of paper and is the parent of posterpaper.
ekaw#Industrial_Session: The industrialsession is a child of the conferencesession and the scientificevent.
ekaw#Conference_Session: The conferencesession is the parent of both the scientificevent and the industrialsession. The conferencebanquet is also the parent of the conferencesession.
ekaw#Regular_Session: The regular session is the child of the session and the parent of the workshop session.
ekaw#Poster_Session: The postersession is the child of the session which is the parent of the demosession.
ekaw#Demo_Session: The demosession is the child of the scientificevent which is the parent of the conferencebanquet.
ekaw#Session: The session is the child of the scientificevent and the socialevent. It is also the parent of the demosession, the postersession and the regularsession.
ekaw#Abstract: The abstract is a child of both paper and tutorialabstract. Paper is the parent of regularpaper and abstract is the child of invitedtalkabstract.
ekaw#Document: The flyer and the website are both parented by the same document. The flyer is the parent of the flyer and the brochure. The conference paper is also parented by the same document.
ekaw#Paper_Author: The paperauthor is the child of the person who is the parent of the agency staff member.
ekaw#Conference_Trip: conferencetrip is a child of socialvent which is the parent of conferencebanquet.
ekaw#Social_Event: Socialvent is the parent of conferencetrip and conferencebanquet. It is also the child of scientificevent and socialvent.
ekaw#Tutorial_Abstract: The abstract is a child of the tutorial abstract which is a child of the document which is parented by paper which is also parented by industrialpaper.
ekaw#Conference_Participant: The child of a conferenceparticipant is a student, the child of a presenter, the child of an invited speaker, the child of a sessionchair, the child of a pcmember, the child of a tutorialchair and the child of a demochair.
ekaw#Submitted_Paper: The parent of submittedpaper is assignedpaper, the parent of acceptedpaper and the parent of posterpaper.
ekaw#Assigned_Paper: The assignedpaper is the child of submittedpaper and acceptedpaper. The assignedpaper is the parent of evaluatedpaper.
ekaw#Negative_Review: The negative review is a child of the flyer and is a parent of the flyer.
ekaw#Review: Review is the parent of neutralreview and negativereview. It is also the child of flyer and document.
ekaw#Neutral_Review: The neutralreview is a child of review which is a parent of the programmebrochure.
ekaw#Organising_Agency: The organisingagency is a child of the organisation which is parented by the academicinstitution which is parented by the researchinstitute.
ekaw#Academic_Institution: The academicinstitution is parented by the organising agency and the university. It is also parented by the researchinstitute.
ekaw#Organisation: The parent organisation of the academicinstitution is the organisingagency. The same organisation is the parent of the researchinstitute and the proceedings publisher.
ekaw#Proceedings_Publisher: The proceedingspublisher is a child of the organisation which is parented by the organisation.
ekaw#Poster_Paper: Posterpaper is a child of paper and is the parent of demopaper.
ekaw#Regular_Paper: Paper is a child of paper and is the parent of industrial paper.
ekaw#Demo_Paper: Demopaper is a child of paper. It is parented by both submittedpaper and assignedpaper. It is also parented by evaluatedpaper.
ekaw#Research_Institute: The researchinstitute is the child of the academicinstitution which is the parent of the university.
ekaw#Scientific_Event: The scientificevent is the parent of the conference and the industrialsession. It is also the parent of the workshop and the conference. It is also the parent of the social event.
ekaw#Invited_Talk_Abstract: The abstract of invitedtalkabstract is child of document which is parented by review and negative review.
ekaw#Agency_Staff_Member: The agency staff member is the child of the person who is the parent of the paperauthor.
ekaw#Workshop_Session: The workshopsession is a child of the scientificevent.
ekaw#Track: The track is the child of scientificevent which is the parent of workshop.
ekaw#Invited_Talk: The child of the invitedtalk and the parent of contributedtalk is the individualpresentation.
ekaw#Workshop: The workshop is the child of scientificevent which is the parent of the conference.
ekaw#Tutorial: The tutorial is child of the individualpresentation which is the parent of the invitedtalk.
ekaw#Contributed_Talk: Contributedtalk is a child of individualpresentation and invitedtalk.
ekaw#Conference: The conference is the child of scientificevent which is the parent of socialvent which is the parent of conferencetrip.
ekaw#Demo_Chair: The demochair is the child of the conferenceparticipant who is the parent of the earlyregistered participant.
ekaw#Tutorial_Chair: The tutorialchair is the child of pcmember and scmember. The conferenceparticipant is a child of a person.
ekaw#PC_Chair: pcchair is the child of the conferenceparticipant and the parent of the tutorialchair. scmember is also a child of pcchair.
ekaw#PC_Member: pcmember is the parent of scmember and workshopchair. pcchair is the child of conferenceparticipant and lateregistered participant. pcchair is the child of possiblereviewer and workshopchair.
ekaw#OC_Member: ocmember is the parent of occhair and conferenceparticipant. pcmember is the parent of sessionchair and workshopchair is the child of pcmember.
ekaw#Proceedings: The conferenceproceedings is the parent of the proceedings which are the child of the multiauthorvolume. The abstract is the parent of the abstract and the abstract is the child of the abstract.
ekaw#Programme_Brochure: The programmebrochure is a child of the document which is the parent of the website.
ekaw#Flyer: The flyer is a child of the document which is the parent of the programmebrochure.
ekaw#Web_Site: The multiauthorvolume is the parent of proceedings and the website is the child of the document.
ekaw#Multi-author_Volume: The multiauthorvolume is the parent of proceedings, conferenceproceedings, abstract and tutorialabstract.
ekaw#Individual_Presentation: Individualpresentation is the parent of invitedtalk and contributedtalk. It is also the child of socialvent and conferencetrip.
ekaw#OC_Chair: occhair is a child of ocmember who is a conference participant.
ekaw#Conference_Banquet: conferencebanquet is a child of socialvent which is the parent of conferencetrip.
ekaw#Workshop_Chair: The workshopchair is the child of pcmember and possiblereviewer. The conferenceparticipant is the parent of sessionchair.
ekaw#Conference_Proceedings: The conferenceproceedings is a child of the proceedings and the multiauthor volume.
ekaw#Session_Chair: The sessionchair is the child of the conferenceparticipant, the presenter and the invited speaker. The pcmember is the parent of the workshopchair.
ekaw#Early-Registered_Participant: The earlyregisteredparticipant is a child of the conferenceparticipant and the parent of the agency staff member.
ekaw#Late-Registered_Participant: The lateregisteredparticipant is the child of the conferenceparticipant and the parent of the demochair.
ekaw#University: The university is a child of the academicinstitution which is a child of the organisation.
ekaw#Possible_Reviewer: pcmember and scmember are parents of the agency staff member. The possiblereviewer is a child of the person who is the parent of the agency staff member.
ekaw#Student: The student is the child of the person who is the parent of the paperauthor.
ekaw#Invited_Speaker: The invited speaker is the child of the presenter and the conference participant.
ekaw#Presenter: The presenter is the parent of the invited speaker and the conferenceparticipant. The lateregistered participant is the parent of the presenter.
ekaw#SC_Member: scmember is the child of pcmember who is the parent of workshopchair.
